#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><para>
#: en/adminarea.xml:1328
msgid ""
"There are several possibilities to transport new emails into the ticket "
"system. One of them is the <link linkend=\"email-receiving-cmd\">otrs."
"PostMaster.pl module</link> that pipes the mails directly into the system. "
"Another possibility is the use of mail accounts which can be administrated "
"through the web interface. The \"PostMaster Mail Accounts\" link on the "
"Admin page loads the management console for the mail accounts (see Figure "
"5.48 below). OTRS supports the mail protocols: POP3, POP3S, IMAP and IMAPS."
msgstr ""
