"den Kunden A für CustomerIDs die Werte \"B;C;\" ein."

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><title>
#: en/external-backends.xml:436
msgid "Use more than one customer backend with OTRS"
msgstr "Verwenden mehrerer Kunden Backends"

#. type: Content of: <chapter><section><section><para>
#: en/external-backends.xml:439
msgid ""
