"im Entwickler-Handbuch auf <ulink url=\"http://doc.otrs.org"
"\"><citetitle>http://doc.otrs.org</citetitle></ulink> innerhalb des Kapitels "
"zu den <ulink url=\"http://doc.otrs.org/developer/3.0/en/html/hacking."
"html#TemplatingMechanism\"><citetitle>Templates</citetitle></ulink>."

